{
  "texts": [
    "Authors collected a database and a corpus of ADRs from Forum-Clinic, a patient-oriented site.",
    "Two annotators labeled drugs, effects and ADR relations in the web posts.",
    "This resource was then used to train a kernel-based method with distant supervision for relation extraction.The DrugSemantics corpus [31] is a collection of summaries of product characteristics (SPCs).",
    "One nurse and two nursing students annotated entities of drug names and attributes (e.g.",
    "unit of measurement, dosage form, route or excipient) manually."
  ]
}